      "detail": "Project capital means the aggregation platform requires dedicated investment in data collection, analytical combination, and distribution infrastructure. This investment is more than operating expenditure but creates the platform capability that generates monopoly value. Project capital covers data pipeline development, analytical engine construction, and customer-facing distribution systems. The capital investment creates the platform that converts mandated openness into commercial monopoly."
