      "detail": "Decisive lead means the first platform to achieve comprehensive aggregation builds an advantage that competitors cannot practically replicate. The combination of data coverage, analytical sophistication, and customer lock-in creates barriers that new entrants cannot overcome. Decisive lead is self-reinforcing because dominant position attracts more data sources and customers. First-mover aggregation advantage is the market-structure expression of the paradox."
